# Excludes for the api image build context.
#
# IMPORTANT: docs/ is NOT excluded — it contains the generated swagger
# package that internal/server/server.go imports as a blank-import side
# effect. Excluding it breaks the Go build.
#
# deploy/ is excluded because the api Dockerfile never COPIes it. If a
# future Dockerfile bakes the Keycloak realm into a custom image, remove
# the deploy/ exclusion below (or use a more specific include).
.git
.gitignore
.env
.env.local
.dockerignore
Dockerfile
docker-compose.yml
README.md
AUDITORIA_TECNICA.md
deploy/
config/
*.md
!docs/**
